\section desc Description
Common algorihtm specific for \ref DataFormats_Candidate "Candidate" types
with HepMC generator particle components.

\subsection interface Public interface
None.

\subsection modules Modules
- HepMCCandidateProducer: produces a collection of reco::Candidate of concrete type 
reco::HepMCCandidate with a HepMC::GenParticle component.
It is possible to specify that only stable particles should be used to 
build candidates setting the boolean parameter <tt>stableOnly</tt>, 
and it is possible to specify a list of particle types to be excluded
with the string list parameter <tt>excludeList</tt>. Charge conjugate particles 
will be excluded as well.
<br><br>
Examples of configuration for the modules is the following:
<pre>
\htmlinclude genCandidates.cfi
</pre>

- GenParticleCandidateProducer:  produces a collection of reco::Candidate of concrete type
reco::GenParticleCandidate representing generator particles.
<br><br>
Examples of configuration for the modules is the following:
<pre>
\htmlinclude genParticleCandidates.cfi
</pre>

